    "chunk_text": "MAARGMAARG - A one-stop national platform for Startups and Mentors to Connect, Time to Innovate Together.\n\nउद्योग संवर्धन और आंतरिक व्यापार विभाग\n\nDEPARTMENT FOR PROMOTION OF INDUSTRY AND INTERNAL TRADE\n\nToll Free Number\n\n1800 115 565\n\n* [HOME](/ \"Home\")\n* [ABOUT](/about-us \"About us\")\n* [Become a mentor](/become-mentor \"Become Mentor\")\n* [Get a Mentor](/get-a-mentor \"Get a Mentor\")\n* [Cohorts](/cohort-program)\n* [FAQs](/faq)\n* [Contact Us](/contactus)\n\n* भारत सरकार\n\n  GOVERNMENT OF INDIA\n* वाणिज्य एवं उद्योग मंत्रालय\n\n  MINISTRY OF COMMERCE AND INDUSTRY\n* उद्योग संवर्धन और आंतरिक व्यापार विभाग\n\n  DEPARTMENT FOR PROMOTION OF INDUSTRY AND INTERNAL TRADE",
